{"tid":1800543,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"屌啦星馬明原來係喺哈薩克做官","createTime":"2019-12-28T02:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T11:25:28.000Z","uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1299587e607297aa34f321843ef7629745792d","tid":1800543,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T02:38:58.000Z","msg":"有生還者表示，客機出事前曾經激烈搖晃，撞到建築物後傳出巨響，機艙內一片漆黑，乘客要用手機照明。事故後，有近十名乘客協助救出其他被困的人。<br />\n<br />\n總統托卡耶夫主持內閣會議，將周六定為全國哀悼日；<span style=\"color: red;\">又委派總理馬明領導調查委員會，</span>在下月10日提交初步調查報告。<br />\n<br />\n副總理斯克利亞爾表示，飛機起飛時機尾曾兩度觸及跑道，顯示起飛時已出現困難。當局已找到客機俗稱「黑盒」的飛行紀錄儀，將循人為或機件故障方向調查事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2e2d6c702d2501baa1ff1067135b071dec6427","tid":1800543,"uid":148002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T02:48:18.000Z","msg":"閲"},{"pid":"db7d41936c188659f07a801c0ed837d2e57049d6","tid":1800543,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"樓豬做完聖誕功課未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0dc53aad220f4a3039bdb8634b637c46162f91","tid":1800543,"uid":272531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"「黃色經濟圈」認證要大家幫手 - 籌款箱計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800571</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57f44e48d38a59c21cc36440c9b5c8d9a015d955","tid":1800543,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:17:36.000Z","msg":"馬明做官呢個gag咁搞笑<br />\n比著以前tvb未比人反 一定勁多正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以唔係我錯 除非唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/no